 Marilyn Zuniga sparked outrage for allowing her third grade class in Orange , New Jersey , to pen letters to murderer Mumia Abu-Jamal , after he collapsed in the bathroom of the State Correctional Institution at Mahanoy .
Abu- AbuJamal is serving a life sentence in prison after he shot Philadelphia police officer Daniel Faulkner in 1981 .
Both her pupils and high school students in the Philadelphia Student Union wrote to the killer .